td-76d8ec: Implement Audit Schemas
Status: [open]
Type: epic | Priority: P2
Labels: audit-schemas

Description:
The HMAC chain module needs persistent storage for audit entries and checkpoints before context logic can read or write records. This epic establishes the database tables, Ecto schemas, indexes, and append-only protections that form the audit data foundation.

Artifacts:
- Proposal: openspec/changes/audit-schemas/proposal.md
- Design: openspec/changes/audit-schemas/design.md
- Tasks: openspec/changes/audit-schemas/tasks.md
- Specs: openspec/changes/audit-schemas/specs/

